you can't make sense of any facial features. 

38
00:02:45,630 --> 00:02:47,743
你分不出谁是谁
You can't tell one person from the other, 

39
00:02:47,744 --> 00:02:48,745
除非通过声音
unless you heard their voice

40
00:02:48,779 --> 00:02:50,747
或他们的其他特征来辨认
or recognized some other part of them.

41
00:02:50,781 --> 00:02:52,300
大脑不像本应该的那样
The brain just doesn't process 

42
