Jilted husband. Maybe Idaris didn't pay protection.

95
00:05:15,651 --> 00:05:17,619
或许他赌博呢
Maybe he gambles.

96
00:05:17,653 --> 00:05:19,854
也没准艾德瑞斯只是随机被选中的受害人
Or, maybe Idaris was just a random victim.

97
00:05:19,888 --> 00:05:21,269
目击者听到了" 我认识你 " 
Witnesses heard "I know you" 

98
00:05:21,270 --> 00:05:22,190
和 " 你认识我 "
or "you know me"?

99
00:05:22,224 --> 00:05:23,824
这么说 你觉得是私人恩怨了
So, you think it's personal.

100
00:05:23,859 --> 00:05:26,693
我希望是 可不想是随机挑选的
I hope it's personal. We don't want random.

101
00:05:26,727 --> 00:05:29,163
你们在干什么 艾德瑞斯呢 他没事吧
What are you doing? Where's Idaris? Is he gonna be OK?

102
00:05:29,197 --> 00:05:32,204
没事 我们的人在医院陪着他
OK, our people are with him over at the hospital. 

103
00:05:32,205 --> 00:05:33,333
他不会有事的
He's gonna be fine.

104
00:05:33,368 --> 00:05:36,336
你们如何处置他的物品 他什么也没干
What were you doing with his stuff? He didn't do anything.

105
00:05:36,371 --> 00:05:38,338
有人袭击了他 我们只是试图找出原因
Someone attacked him. We're just trying to figure out why.

106
00:05:38,373 --> 00:05:40,673
