- 你叫什么名字 - 茱莉娅
- What's your name? - Julia.

110
00:05:46,213 --> 00:05:48,481
茱莉娅 你知道有谁想伤害你老板吗
Julia, do you know anyone who'd want to hurt your boss?

111
00:05:48,515 --> 00:05:51,651
不知道 人人都爱艾德瑞斯
No. Everybody loves Idaris.

112
00:05:51,685 --> 00:05:54,853
调查警司 我找到些东西
Detective Sergeant? I found something.

113
