Get the hell out of here! You'll blow your fingers off!

115
00:06:09,702 --> 00:06:11,536
嘿 艾登 你还好吧
Yo, Aidan. You cool?

116
00:06:13,871 --> 00:06:15,339
没事 伙计
Yeah, man.

117
00:06:15,373 --> 00:06:17,874
只是有点神经质 仅此而已
Just a little jumpy, that's all.

118
00:06:20,312 --> 00:06:22,079
还在做团体倾诉治疗吗
Still doing that group thing?

119
00:06:22,113 --> 00:06:24,748
