- You want to take care of that? - Yeah.

121
00:06:49,472 --> 00:06:51,440
貌似他不止记不住面孔
Seems like it's not just faces he can't remember.

122
00:06:51,474 --> 00:06:53,842
他有短期记忆问题
He has short-term memory problems.

123
00:06:53,876 --> 00:06:55,844
人面失认症可能更大部分是
The prosopagnosia could be part of larger

124
00:06:55,878 --> 00:06:57,128
神经退行性问题 
neurodegenerative issues. 

125
00:06:57,129 --> 00:06:58,880
打扰一下 我们能帮上忙吗
Excuse me. Can we help you?

126
00:06:58,914 --> 00:07:01,415
我看着像需要帮忙吗
Uh, oh, do I look like I need help?

127
00:07:01,450 --> 00:07:04,118
我们正处于评估的中间环节 如果您能
We're just in the middle of an assessment. If you could

128
