He's heading into the middle stages. 

146
00:07:54,165 --> 00:07:55,466
他的记忆浮现又消失
His memory comes and goes.

147
00:07:55,501 --> 00:07:57,968
这么说 他明天或许会记得更多喽
So, he might remember more tomorrow?

148
00:07:58,003 --> 00:07:59,970
