我不知道你在说什么
I don't know what you're talking about.

674
00:36:02,340 --> 00:36:05,142
是艾德瑞斯让你这么做的吗
Did Idaris tell you to do that?

675
00:36:07,145 --> 00:36:11,649
你杀得够多 就学会不再哭泣
That if you did it enough times, you'd learn not to cry?

676
00:36:13,651 --> 00:36:17,019
是他告诉你要从那些动物身上汲取力量吗
Did he tell you that you'd take on the strength of those animals?

677
00:36:17,053 --> 00:36:21,190
因为那是个谎言 茱莉娅 我觉得你是知道的
Because that's a lie, Julia, and I think you know it.

678
00:36:21,224 --> 00:36:26,196
他在别的地方跟其他孩子也说这个谎
And that's a lie that he's told other kids in other places.

679
00:36:28,698 --> 00:36:31,300
我知道他跟你说你是特别的
And I know that he told you that you are special,

680
00:36:31,334 --> 00:36:32,934
但你确实是特别的 茱莉娅
and you are special, Julia,

681
00:36:32,968 --> 00:36:34,869
不过不是对他而言
but not to him.

682
00:36:37,674 --> 00:36:41,443
我每天跟罪犯打交道
I deal with people who commit crimes every day.

683
00:36:41,477 --> 00:36:42,944
有一些
Some...

684
00:36:42,978 --> 00:36:45,646
是好人做了坏事
are good people who have done bad things,

685
00:36:45,681 --> 00:36:48,081
而另外一些
but others...

686
00:36:53,021 --> 00:36:57,425
多数精神病学家不相信善恶
Most psychiatrists don't believe in good and evil.

687
00:36:57,459 --> 00:36:59,026
但是我信
But I do.

688
00:37:01,028 --> 00:37:02,995
并且据我所知
And the one thing I have learned

689
00:37:03,030 --> 00:37:05,398
善恶之间并无高墙
is there is no great wall between them.

690
00:37:05,433 --> 00:37:09,068
如果你能跨步出线
If you can step over the line...

691
00:37:09,102 --> 00:37:11,871
那么也能退后
You can step back.

692
00:37:14,542 --> 00:37:16,875
我知道你是个好人
I know you're a good person.

693
00:37:16,909 --> 00:37:19,110
我也知道如果不是为了艾德瑞斯
And I know you wouldn't have done these things

694
00:37:19,145 --> 00:37:20,979
你也不会做这些事情
if it wasn't for Idaris,

695
00:37:22,982 --> 00:37:25,650
但是我要听你说出来
But I need to hear it from you.

696
00:37:29,988 --> 00:37:31,504
他跟我说这是保护他
He told me that it was the only way 

697
00:37:31,505 --> 00:37:34,325
免受敌人迫害的唯一方式
to protect him from his enemies.

698
00:37:45,169 --> 00:37:47,671
他告诉我必须杀死布鲁克曼医生
He told me I had to kill Dr. Bruckmann.

699
00:38:08,992 --> 00:38:10,960
监视汇报说艾德瑞斯出门了
Surveillance said Idaris just left his house,

700
00:38:10,994 --> 00:38:12,719
去了茱莉娅家 跟祖母谈了一下
went to Julia's, spoke to the grandmother, 

701
00:38:12,720 --> 00:38:13,963
现在他向西奔着邓达斯去了
now he's headed west on Dundas.

702
00:38:13,997 --> 00:38:16,132
他要逃跑 或许会去机场方向
He's gonna make a run for it. Probably headed to the airport.

703
00:38:16,166 --> 00:38:19,100
我打赌 是信用社 他要跑路 一定需要钱
My bet, the credit union. If he's gonna rabbit, he'll need money.

704
00:38:19,135 --> 00:38:20,636
我们去那儿
Let's get there.

705
00:38:28,010 --> 00:38:31,179
- 进展如何 - 他要出来了
- How we doing? - He's coming out now.

706
00:39:44,482 --> 00:39:46,550
现在你认识我了吗
You recognize me now?

707
00:39:48,520 --> 00:39:51,154
艾登 艾登 抓住他了
Aidan! Aidan, I got him!

708
00:39:53,491 --> 00:39:55,525
抓住他了
I got him.

709
00:40:23,519 --> 00:40:27,487
# 你咆哮发出的回音 #
The echo to your yell

710
00:40:27,522 --> 00:40:31,592
# 你潜水产生的涟漪 #
The ripple to your dive

711
00:40:32,626 --> 00:40:37,598
# 你摇摆下的涌流 #
The currents under your wave

712
00:40:37,933 --> 00:40:40,267
你是茱莉娅吗
You're Julia?

713
00:40:40,301 --> 00:40:43,670
对
Yes.

714
00:40:43,704 --> 00:40:46,306
你吓坏了
You're frightened.

715
00:41:00,220 --> 00:41:02,188
谢谢
Thank you.

716
00:41:02,222 --> 00:41:05,757
如果你愿意 我可以去探望你
And I could come to visit you, if you like.

717
00:41:05,792 --> 00:41:09,695
好 我很愿意
Yeah, I would.

718
00:41:09,729 --> 00:41:12,764
来吧 茱莉娅
Come on, Julia.

719
00:41:12,799 --> 00:41:14,300
该走了
It's time to go.

720
00:41:16,969 --> 00:41:20,305
# 我能感觉到你 #
I could feel you

721
00:41:20,339 --> 00:41:23,874
# 包围着我 #
All around me

722
00:41:32,750 --> 00:41:34,718
要把她怎么着
What will happen to her?

723
00:41:34,752 --> 00:41:36,720
她还未成年
Well, she's a minor,

724
00:41:36,754 --> 00:41:39,889
而且会考虑艾德瑞斯的影响因素
and Idaris' influence will be taken into account,

725
00:41:39,924 --> 00:41:42,759
所以她仍有机会享受美好人生
so she's still got a chance at a good life.

726
00:41:42,793 --> 00:41:44,794
你也一样 本
So do you, Ben.

727
00:41:47,164 --> 00:41:50,366
所以我才逃跑 所以我才来这里
That is why I escaped, why I came here.

728
00:41:52,369 --> 00:41:54,737
我已经没机会了
I haven't had the chance yet.

729
00:41:54,771 --> 00:41:56,739
本 我们已经跟检察官谈过了
Ben, we've been talking to the prosecutors.

730
00:41:56,773 --> 00:41:59,775
他们会重新定罪
They're going to reconsider the charges.

731
00:41:59,809 --> 00:42:00,777
可是与此同时
But in the meantime, 

732
00:42:00,778 --> 00:42:02,945
你必须得去做些心理辅导
you're going to have to get some counselling.

733
00:42:02,979 --> 00:42:04,646
多倾诉
More talk.

734
00:42:04,680 --> 00:42:08,650
倾诉不是软弱 本 躲藏才是
Talking is not a weakness, Ben; hiding is.

735
00:42:10,653 --> 00:42:14,289
我安排人来做你的倾诉对象
I'll make some arrangements to find someone for you to talk with.

736
00:42:14,323 --> 00:42:17,272
在此之前 你若愿意参加小组倾诉 
And until then, if you want to just sit in on a group.

737
00:42:17,273 --> 00:42:20,494
也可以 交给我
It's OK. Uh... I got it.

738
00:42:22,497 --> 00:42:25,332
艾登 你今天带了个朋友啊
Aidan, you brought a friend today.

739
00:42:25,367 --> 00:42:27,834
对 各位 这是本
Yeah. Everyone, this is Ben.

740
00:42:27,869 --> 00:42:29,170
你好 本
Hi, Ben.

741
00:42:31,540 --> 00:42:33,641
你当过兵吗
You were a soldier?

742
00:42:35,643 --> 00:42:39,245
对 在刚果民主共和国
Yes. In the Democratic Republic of Congo.

743
00:42:41,848 --> 00:42:45,017
对 本是来 他只是来倾听的
Yeah, Ben's just... he's just here to listen.

744
00:42:45,052 --> 00:42:48,754
好吧 如果本是来倾听的
Well, if Ben's going to listen, 

745
00:42:48,755 --> 00:42:50,557
那他得有倾听对象啊
he's going to need someone to listen to.

746
00:42:50,591 --> 00:42:52,957
有人想说说吗
Does anyone have anything to say?

747
00:42:52,992 --> 00:42:55,294
有 我有话要说
Yeah. I'll go.

748
00:42:58,231 --> 00:43:01,099
我已经越来越好 进步很多
you know, I've been doing better. A lot better.

749
00:43:01,133 --> 00:43:04,769
但是这周 由于某些原因
Uh... but this week, for some reason,

750
00:43:04,804 --> 00:43:07,038
那种感觉又回来了
it's been coming back on me, and...

751
00:43:07,073 --> 00:43:09,807
每当我睡觉时
when I sleep...

752
00:43:09,841 --> 00:43:11,475
如果我睡着了
if I sleep - uh...

753
00:43:11,510 --> 00:43:16,213
那些最糟糕的事就回来了
the worst things come back.

754
00:43:16,247 --> 00:43:18,248
想跟我们谈谈那些最糟糕的事吗 艾登
Do you want to tell us about the worst things, Aidan?

755
00:43:18,282 --> 00:43:19,705
可是 没什么新鲜的
Well, I mean, it's nothing new. 

756
00:43:19,706 --> 00:43:21,218
你们以前都听过
You guys have heard it all before.

757
00:43:21,252 --> 00:43:23,253
他没听过
He hasn't.

758
00:43:23,287 --> 00:43:26,089
# 从未见过你 #
Never saw you

759
00:43:26,123 --> 00:43:30,992
# 从未听过你消息 #
Never heard you

760
00:43:31,027 --> 00:43:33,895
# 可我知道你就在那里 #
But I knew that you were there

